snippet.title: Star Chasers Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for "Star Chasers", an upcoming action adventure game for iOS and Android platforms.

Join Star Chasers and help rescue the fallen stars before darkness destroys them forever!

Download on the App Store
https://itunes.apple.com/app/the-star-chasers/id959747571

or Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Lightbound.StarChasers
